data.description: Well maintained, large 4 bedroom home w/ awesome floor plan & over 2300 square feet!  This "one owner home" is a great find & features formal living and formal dining rooms, spacious great room w/ high ceiling that flows nicely into the quaint breakfast nook and pretty kitchen area.  The "cook lovers" kitchen has Corian countertops, a pantry closet, a breakfast bar for casual dining and is complete with all of the appliances.  The home has a triple split BR plan w/ all nice sized rooms.  The master suite features two walk-in closets, a garden tub, a step-in shower and dual vanity sink areas.  Additionally, the home has an inside laundry room w/ washer/dryer included, a 2 car garage, a nice screened patio overlooking the back yard, a sprinkler system for the lawn on a separate reclaimed water meter, a security system, an in-wall pest control system, a water softener system & more!  You won't want miss seeing this one!
